    },
    {
      "heading": "题解",
      "level": 2,
      "blocks": [
        {
          "heading": "1. 题目简述",
          "level": 3,
          "blocks": [
            {
              "type": "p",
              "html": "<strong>交互题</strong>。有一棵包含 $N$ 个节点的隐藏树。",
              "depth": 1
            },
            {
              "type": "p",
              "html": "你可以进行询问 <code>? r</code>，系统会返回节点 $r$ 到树上所有其他节点的距离数组。",
              "depth": 1
            },
            {
              "type": "p",
              "html": "你需要通过不超过 $\\lceil \\frac{N}{2} \\rceil$ 次询问，还原出这棵树的所有边。",
              "depth": 1
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "heading": "2. 思维路径：为什么是二分图？",
          "level": 3,
          "blocks": [
            {
              "heading": "线索一：询问一次能得到什么？",
              "level": 4,
              "blocks": [
                {
                  "type": "p",
                  "html": "当我们询问 <code>? r</code> 时，我们得到了 $r$ 到所有点的距离。",
                  "depth": 1
                },
                {
                  "type": "p",
                  "html": "所有距离为 $1$ 的点，必定与 $r$ 直接相连。",
                  "depth": 1
                },
                {
                  "type": "p",
                  "html": "这意味着：<strong>只要询问一个点，我们就能确定所有与它相连的边。</strong>",
                  "depth": 1
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "heading": "线索二：如何覆盖所有边？",
              "level": 4,
              "blocks": [
                {
                  "type": "p",
                  "html": "如果要确定整棵树的所有边，最笨的办法是把 $N$ 个点全问一遍。但这超过了 $\\lceil N/2 \\rceil$ 的限制。",
                  "depth": 1
                },
                {
                  "type": "p",
                  "html": "<strong>我们需要选出一个</strong> $\\lceil N/2 \\rceil$ <strong>大小的点集 S，使得树上的每一条边，至少有一个端点在 S 中</strong>。",
                  "depth": 1
                },
                {
                  "type": "p",
                  "html": "如果一条边的两个端点都在 $S$ 中，问谁都能发现这条边。",
                  "depth": 2
                },
                {
                  "type": "p",
                  "html": "如果一条边只有一个端点在 $S$ 中，问那个端点就能发现这条边。",
                  "depth": 2
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "heading": "线索三：树的特殊结构",
              "level": 4,
              "blocks": [
                {
                  "type": "p",
                  "html": "树是一个<strong>二分图</strong>，把树按<strong>黑白染色</strong>后，也十分适合 $\\lceil N/2 \\rceil$ 的限制。",
                  "depth": 1
                },
                {
                  "type": "p",
                  "html": "这是树最本质的性质之一：树上的节点可以被染成黑色和白色，使得<strong>所有的边都是连接一黑一白的</strong>。",
                  "depth": 1
                },
                {
                  "type": "p",
                  "html": "<strong>如何染色？</strong>",
                  "depth": 1
                },
                {
                  "type": "p",
                  "html": "如果我们定节点 $1$ 为根：",
                  "depth": 2
                },
                {
                  "type": "p",
                  "html": "距离为 $0$（根）：黑色",
                  "depth": 3
                },
                {
                  "type": "p",
                  "html": "距离为 $1$（儿子）：白色",
                  "depth": 3
                },
                {
                  "type": "p",
                  "html": "距离为 $2$（孙子）：黑色",
                  "depth": 3
                },
                {
                  "type": "p",
                  "html": "距离为 $3$：白色",
                  "depth": 3
                },
                {
                  "type": "p",
                  "html": "...",
                  "depth": 3
                },
                {
                  "type": "p",
                  "html": "你会发现：<strong>节点的深度的奇偶性，天然决定了它的颜色！</strong>",
                  "depth": 1
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "heading": "结论",
          "level": 3,
          "blocks": [
            {
              "type": "p",
              "html": "由于所有的边都是“黑-白”连接：",
              "depth": 1
            },
            {
              "type": "p",
              "html": "如果我们询问所有的<strong>黑点</strong>，<strong>因为每条边都连着黑点，我们能还原所有边。</strong>",
              "depth": 2
            },
            {
              "type": "p",
              "html": "如果我们询问所有的<strong>白点</strong>，<strong>因为每条边都连着白点，我们也能还原所有边。</strong>",
              "depth": 2
            },
            {
              "type": "p",
              "html": "这就是解题的核心：<strong>我们要么问完所有奇数深度的点，要么问完所有偶数深度的点。哪边人少，就问哪边。</strong>",
              "depth": 1
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "heading": "代码",
      "level": 2,
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "code",
          "lang": "cpp",
          "code": "vector<int> g[N];\nint dis[N][N];\nint n;\nbool vis[N][N];\nvoid Q(int x) {\n\tcout << \"? \" << x << endl;\n\tcout.flush();\n\tfa(i, 1, n)cin >> dis[x][i];\n}\nvoid A() {\n\tcout << \"!\" << endl;\n\tfa(i, 1, n)fa(j, 1, n)vis[i][j] = 0;\n\tfa(i, 1, n)for (int to : g[i]) {\n\t\tif (!vis[i][to]) {\n\t\t\tvis[i][to] = vis[to][i] = 1;\n\t\t\tcout << i << ' ' << to << endl;\n\t\t}\n\t}\n\tcout.flush();\n}\nvoid solve(int CASE)\n{\n\tcin >> n;\n\tint cnt = n - 1;\n\n\tQ(1);\n\tint _1 = 0;\n\tfa(i, 1, n) {\n\t\tif (dis[1][i] == 1 and !vis[1][i]) {\n\t\t\tvis[1][i] = vis[i][1] = 1;\n\t\t\tg[1].pb(i), g[i].pb(1);\n\t\t\tcnt--;\n\t\t}\n\n\t\tif (dis[1][i] & 1)_1++;\n\t\tif (!cnt) {\n\t\t\tA();\n\t\t\tbreak;\n\t\t}\n\t}\n\n\tvar ve = vector<int>();\n\tif (_1 <= n - 1 - _1) {\n\t\tfa(i, 1, n)\n\t\t\tif (dis[1][i] & 1)\n\t\t\t\tve.pb(i);\n\t}\n\telse {\n\t\tfa(i, 1, n)\n\t\t\tif (dis[1][i] % 2 == 0 and i != 1)\n\t\t\t\tve.pb(i);\n\t}\n\n\tfor (int now : ve) {\n\t\tQ(now);\n\n\t\tfa(i, 1, n) {\n\t\t\tif (dis[now][i] == 1 and !vis[now][i]) {\n\t\t\t\tvis[now][i] = vis[i][now] = 1;\n\t\t\t\tg[now].pb(i), g[i].pb(now);\n\t\t\t\tcnt--;\n\t\t\t}\n\n\t\t\tif (!cnt) {\n\t\t\t\tA();\n\t\t\t\tbreak;\n\t\t\t}\n\t\t}\n\t}\n\treturn;\n}",
          "depth": 1
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
